content.rendered:
The Phuket Outdoor Lounge Set is made from premium commercial grade Win-Tech flat weave rattan, with Rust Proof 1.5 mm aluminium frame. The Win-Tech rattan also means that there is minimum maintenance required and is totally weatherproof and easy to keep clean.

This 4 seater Set is perfect for patio’s, gardens and busy pubs, hotels and bars.

Attractive brown/black weave and tempered glass table top make the Jakarta a solid choice for busy commercial venues.

Cushions included in the set! (Cushions are shower proof & machine washable). 

This item arrives fully assembled and comes with a 2 year guarantee. Ideal for indoor or outdoor use.

Table: L:1160mm, D:600mm, H:450mm. Chair: L:780mm, D:780mm, H:690mm. Sofa: L:1360mm, D:780mm, H:690mm.
